      • GET_NEXT_OBJECT_LIST

        public static final DataCBType GET_NEXT_OBJECT_LIST
        Bit flag for getting a List of objects using an iterator retrieved from the DpDataCallback.iterator(DpTrans,ConfObject[]) method. Each object being an represented as an array of ConfValue. This method is used for large lists where sending data in bigger chunks is preferable.
